    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>halved shallot</strong>,<strong> pepper strips</strong>,<strong> halved ginger </strong>and<strong> crushed garlic </strong>to the dish with your <strong>berbere seasoning</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add 450ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[600ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[750ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> with the <strong>beef stock mix </strong>and<strong> </strong>1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
